<h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Privacy Policy</h1>

<div class="govuk-body">

    <p>
        This website is committed to protecting your privacy in accordance with UK data protection legislation, including the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the Privacy and Electronic Communications Regulations (PECR).
    </p>

    <p>
        We collect standard internet log information and details of visitor behavior patterns using analytics tools. This helps us understand how the site is used and improve our services. Analytics data is collected in a way that does not directly identify anyone. We do not make any attempt to find out the identities of those visiting our website.
    </p>

    <p>
        Where cookies are used for analytics, you will be informed and given the option to accept or decline non-essential cookies. Essential cookies, necessary for the operation of the site, are set automatically.
    </p>

    <p>
        Any personal data you provide will be processed lawfully, fairly, and transparently. We will not share your information with third parties unless required by law. For more details on how your data is handled, your rights, and how to contact us, please refer to our full privacy notice.
    </p>

